prompt.title: Embedding for Simple Book Markdown Language Guide
prompt.content: The Book language is designed to be a strict subset of markdown, easy to read and write, and understandable by both humans and machines without specific knowledge of the language. It uses .book.md or .book file extensions with UTF-8 non-BOM encoding.
